%ABn/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-07/poem-rrNwYSvPK5AaH5Hi4d_niA">Trúc chi từ kỳ 07 - 竹枝詞其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/author-o4EVPW8qBqGIiDBnjz0VQg">Vương Quang Duẫn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/T%E1%BB%AD-V%C5%A9-Kim-L%C4%83ng-k%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-t1bKnegpWvBEP7LcwIXKCg">Tử Vũ Kim Lăng ký Hồng Kiều thi kỳ 1 - 子羽金陵寄紅橋詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-poKMVsKTu5nOsOOtpFmCOA">Tương quân - 湘君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/%E1%BB%A8c-giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ng%C3%B4-x%E1%BB%AD-s%C4%A9/poem-BpmzAGJvrymZfyytily7-w">Ức giang thượng Ngô xử sĩ - 憶江上吳處士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/author-zlEhGhvit8FPpDIsa8T0QA">Giả Đảo</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
